\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you tell me your full name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Florence Kate Johnson. Known as Norrie. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And your address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 23, Leafield Avenue.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 1892.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Battersea I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't know that I was born there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know which house you first lived in or where the first house you lived in was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, that was in Battersea. We -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you tell me the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Near Christchurch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How long did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh - about seventeen years perhaps. Probably. I should think so, I don't know whether I was born there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did you move to after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Clapham Common then. North Side, Clapham Common.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How long did you live at that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Until we came here in 1938.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So you've really only lived in three houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 In three houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know why you moved from Battersea to Clapham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - I think mother just thought she'd like something different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Two brothers only.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were they older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Yes, much older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How much older were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh - seven years quite.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The eldest one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh five or six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 He was eighty when he died. I don't know how old he would be when I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What year did he die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 1939.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mottesfont. And before that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4997532\charrsid5785238 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238  Abbott}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4997532\charrsid5785238 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 s Ann in Hampshire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 He 
was a - correspondent clerk I think. The - Southern Railway, it used to be called the London and South Western Railway. Clerk I think. Correspondence clerk. I think, something like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would that mean that he wrote the letters in connection with the railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Wrote the letters. Yes, with the - traffic staff, parcels and - things I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he have another job before or after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No. No. No, only that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember him ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't know but she was - seventy-eight, I think, when she died. That was in 193 - 7.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 She came from Chertsey, in Hampshire. I think it's Hampshire, no, or Surrey. Surrey. Chertsey in Surrey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Had she any jobs before she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, she was - telegraphist in a Post Office. She used to do the telegrams. On a little thing like this.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did she work after she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The house where you lived in Battersea, can you tell me how many rooms there were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Two - three - oh something like this I should think. Three bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And two rooms downstairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm. And a kitchen. Bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and you live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not at that stage. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did she later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How much later, before the end of 1918 or after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh probably - after, I should think after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Yes, it was done at home, yes. Well most of it, not all of it. Mm. Yes. Mother did what there was mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 That went to the - some sort of laundry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother or father make or mend the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh mother did, yes, father wouldn't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did she make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, she never made. She wasn't awfully good at needlework.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were the clothes new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4997532\charrsid5785238  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 New.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you know where they were bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 My things used to home from Peter Jones in - Chelsea, or Arding and Hobbs at Clapham Junction.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When did you have new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh that I don't remember at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No special time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Easter would be - an occ
asion, you had new clothes for Easter in those days. But apart from that, and then - when the autumn came I would have a - different weight hat and coat.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about shoes, did your mother or father make or mend those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I - I always had expen
sive shoes because I'd got a long aristocratic foot. And you couldn't get cheap shoes to fit. I've always had to pay a lot of money for shoes, apart from these you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were they shoes or boots?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Shoes mostly. Yes, boots weren't so fashionable then. You didn't have Wellington like you do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. But he did the gardening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he do any decorating or make fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Fires, yes, not decorating as a rule I don't think,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he ever look after you, bath you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Don't remember him doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he take you out without your mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Used to take me to the Battersea Park, and there was always a chrysanthemum show every year I remember we went to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Just you or your brothers as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, that would be me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he ever look after you when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Don't remember it, I don't think mother ever went out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your brothers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have to do any little jobs for your brothers because they were older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I think so. I can't remember - reasonably early I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know what age you put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you share the bedroom with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You had a room to yourself and the boys had a room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 They shared a room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You had a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How often did you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh about twice a week I should think, I don't remember - it being a ritual.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well mostly in the kitchen. Big - kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was there any occasion when they ate in another room?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 In the dining room, yes. Perhaps at party or guests coming.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Kitchen. Or scullery. We had a scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Separate from the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm. No, I think the - the - the - kitchen - stove would be in the kitchen. We didn't have a gas stove then. Not in the early days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was this a range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I can't remember - early I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What members of the family were present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I can't recollect sitting down to breakfast but I suppose we all did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember what you usually ate or drank for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh it would be tea, we didn't have a lot of coffee. And - things in the bacon and egg line.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about the midday meal, what was that called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well in the early days it would be dinner when I was - babyish. Dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When would you have that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 That would be I suppose about one o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was all the family present for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I should - I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 During the week would your father come home for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Father came home for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you come home from school for dinner?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And your brothers as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't know about my brothers. I don't think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What would one eat for midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh sort of roast lamb or - beefsteak pudding or stews or - more that than anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would you have anything different on certain days for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Roast beef perhaps on Sunday with apple pie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about the evening meal, what would that be called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Well that would be more high tea if we'd had a - a dinner midday. Later on we had a - a lunch, well then we had dinner at seven. When we were coming home from work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 But before that you had high tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What would one eat for high tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - probably fish or - something in that line, I can't remember - exactly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Make jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not at that time, no. Nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Pickled onions.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Make wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Any medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. Nothing at all like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was any beer brewed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. An aunt made ginger beer. But it went off in the cupboard - with a l
oud explosion. Frightened the life out of us. It was rather horrid actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, we used to get all our stuff from grandmother who lived just opposite Mottesfont Abbey in - Hampshire again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever have tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
No. Tinned fruit came later. But no - vegetables, nothing in that line, no. I don't know whether it was made, sardines I suppose we got. But there was very little tinned food abo
ut. And mother wasn't addicted to it, but she liked the better quality tinned fruit - the poaches and - things like that. That was later, that wasn't when I was a baby I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would this be before the end of the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I doubt it. I don't know. I should say after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your family keep any livestock, hens or pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
No. No. No, nothing like that. We had a cat or a dog I think. No, well grandmother had a very large garden and she had all these hens, we always got our eggs from there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 From Hampshire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 That was quite a long way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Came up in the train. The - box of eggs. And sometimes a - a hamper and then there would be - various things in it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh pretty well every day. Oh yes, I would say without exception every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever get some extra meat such as rabbit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, frequently, that came up from - quite often from Hampshire or - Ex - Exeter. I'd got an uncle at Exeter. He se
nt two rabbits up. And then we used to get a brace of pheasants from - Dorset I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 For example, if you children liked anything particularly would she go without so you could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - you wouldn't notice it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh yes. Yes, she wasn't a bit strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to have a little bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh no, you chose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I never remember that there was any row about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask someone to pass it or did you have to wait 'til it was offered?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh you could ask.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and to sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I think you did that by instinct, I don't ever remember being taught a lot of things. I think it's inborn in you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 If you were slouching at all would you get into trouble or did that never occur?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I've never heard it applied to me, well - if I do, it's - it's a thing I can't remember, but I can hear other children being told.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - there again I can't remember. I - I suppose when we'd finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How was the meal served, or by whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What order were you served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I couldn't say. No. Don't remember that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was she a motherly person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, she was very good natured with a tremendous sense of humour. They always say I'm like her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was she an affectionate person, did she show affection?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 If you had any worries could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't remember that, perhaps I didn't have any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was your father an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Very easy. Very easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he have a sense of humour as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, not particularly, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was he affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, not noticeably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 It was never mentioned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did they bring you up to behave towards your brothers in a special way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, nothing - nothing was - I can't ever remember anything being said about behaviour. I think I must have been very uninteresting.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know what kind of person your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did they think certain things were right or wrong, that some things were important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, well mother was a bit high church. Father used to - sing in the choir and ring the 
bell - with the - the ringers, I think they must have been short because he started at the age of ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And he did this when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, no. No. No, this was his age - his child - child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So they felt religion was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
It wasn't mentioned. Well there wasn't so much of that - as there is now you know, nothing like. I don't think you heard it to any extent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, I think if we wanted to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 If you did something your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - the only time I think mother disapproved was when I picked up my - ra}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4997532\charrsid5785238 ck}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 et and went to play tennis on Sunday but she didn't say a word, but she just looked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 She didn't say anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. But I was older then of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember ever being told off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I can't - I can't think anything - was ever said like that, there was no shouting and rowing and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were they ever spanked or sent to bed early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. Don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4997532\charrsid5785238  ever remember them being mischie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 vous?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, I can't actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both parents or did one play a more important part in your life?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I can't recollect ever anything coming into my life about that, as I say it's - I think it's instinct in you. Seems to me it must be.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I had a little party. And presents.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember anything you did with your mother or father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, we were at home of course. But - they used to take me to Hampton Court and Windsor Castle for outings. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Any time during the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
In - more perhaps the summer holidays. I liked that. Mother was very fond of buildings, well I am now. I like these stately homes. Of course you couldn't go in - them then. Not in those days. You could -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 But you could go to Hampton Court?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, Hampton Court Palace. And - the Queen Charlote's Palace in Kew Gardens we went to quite a lot. And Windsor Castle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father go with you as well on those outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Sometimes, it depended if we went on a weekday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were the boys interested in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't think they ever came with us, I expect they were doing something else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You were at home for Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Always for holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever have any relatives or other people coming to spend Christmas with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't think so. I can't remember that we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I was eight when I started to learn the piano, that was the old one we got rid of - a few years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did anybody else play the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Yes, both my brothers, they played better than me. And then when they were a little bit older and wanted to learn dancing we used to have a dance on a Saturday night. In the front room.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 With other people as well, other young people would come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, well not properly, but - for birthdays and parties everybody would sing something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Individually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Individually. Yes, there wasn't community singing, not in the early days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you and your family ever sing together, some evenings would one of you play and the others sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not together, but - father used to - be induced to sing at these parties you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh used to play cards a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Any outdoor games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. Cricket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 They'd play cricket with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Father would play cricket with us in Battersea Park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were there books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Books? Yes, but - they didn't read a tremendous lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember your mother or father reading aloud to you or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't - I don't, no. Oh yes, father did I can remember, that's going back. But what it was I don't know, I know he laughed a lot.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were there newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Oh yes, all newspapers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Magazines in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not so many, not what they call the glossy magazines. But was the - The Windsor magazine. And the Pall Mall magazine. Wha
t else was there. Always Punch of course. But the - the - ordinary - I - I suppose - Daily Mail and - there was a Morning Post I think. The - sporting papers. Sporting Life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember a funeral in the family before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I never went to one. But - two uncles died I think. I didn't go to a funeral myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Who would take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mother. Relations used to give parties, we all went to. Then when we were 
a little bit older my brothers got up a minstrel show. They copied - there was - not the present Black and White Minstrels but there were some - minstrels of some sort, I should have thought that - I don't know that was before the great war, I should have
 thought it was. So they copied that quite a lot. Was rather fun.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So you had quite a lot of young people around your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Relations you see, I'd got a good many relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mainly relations rather than friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Just a few friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not a lot, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
You said that your parents used to take you to Hampston Court and Windsor, can you remember anywhere else you went, would you go anywhere special on a Bank Holiday for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I can remember going to an Aunt Mance at - Barnes, Barnes Common, well then we'd go on the Common and - play rounders probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not always. We went to Brighton and - and Exeter to the relations.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The whole family went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
I don't think the boys went, yes, they were a bit older I think. But - we didn't go to a hotel like you did later, well I don't think there were so many. More boarding houses of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh well frankly I can't remember that I did anything. No. Nothing out of the ordinary. Nothing comes back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Sundays, well we went to church, in my very young days that would be Christchurch. And when - when I moved - that would
 be Ascension church, that was Anglo-Catholic more. I liked that. And then St Mary's was the next one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go once every Sunday or more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mostly, yes, up until the war here, this last war of course - you didn't know whether you'd be a - awake or a sleep. I did go sometimes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have to wear different clothes on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Usually. Well perhaps always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, not until I went to that tennis, I was older then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
They didn't actually say so. And there wasn't this - fierce - sort of - Baptist touch where you mustn't read or - do anything. Our home wasn't like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents go to church with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not as a rule. Mother used to go to the Ascension. But - not when I was a baby I don't remember them going so much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 That was Church of England, the Ascension?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. I was taken as a guest but I never became a member.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go to any other social activities organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
No, not in those days I don't think. No, I can't - my two brothers were choir boys, I daresay they did things. It didn't occur to me to sort of - register anything to remember. About them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, I - he was - he was always a Conservative, quite interested in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know why he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, he never became an active - member, like they do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You can't remember him campaigning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I - I'm sure he didn't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother take an interest in it as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well only in - talking about it you see, there was no vote - for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember your father voting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh always, yes. Oh yes, he wouldn't have missed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 In some places at that time men felt that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Never heard that. May have been so, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time? What would adults do with their leisure time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - makes you wonder doesn't it n
ow when you think back but - they did something. There wasn't so much to do. There was no cinema you see. No television I don't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did they read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - suppose they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Sew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - I didn't see what went on after I went to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not - not apart from relations and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not a lot, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When did your father get home from work in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh about - oh just before six I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How many evenings would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh every one. Mostly anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he attend any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. He didn't belong to anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
He liked to go but I - I - you wouldn't say he attended them at that time, it was later. When - when I was older. He would like to go. Yes, he quite liked watching that. Would go to Epsom or - Hurst Park, something near.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Only in small - very small amounts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, like boot clubs or sick clubs or funeral clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How did you get on with your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you feel particularly close to one of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 As a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I don't know, meself I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were there any little neighbours nearby that you used to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, they didn't come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh we had a garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever play in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No. I wasn't allowed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Chiefly with a ball and bat and - that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You liked cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well there again, my - nobody nagged us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you free to play with anyone you please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you discouraged from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you think of anybody in particular or why you were discouraged from playing with other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, we just didn't play in the street you see, it wasn't done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, there weren't any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 All - we - usually we had a dog - and a cat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you collect anything or do gardening or have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, father did the garden. I - I seem to have had a very uneventful life I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I've always been a great walker, but of course not at that time that you're talking about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Yes, father taught me to ride a bicycle in - Battersea Park when I was about nine or ten. I used to go out then until - the motor buses got on the road. And discouraged us, I gave it up then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I never did fishing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not until I was older when I played tennis.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When you say older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - when I went to the Water Board, joined their sports club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go to any theatres or concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Yes, there was - a Shakespeare theatre at that time on Lavender Hill in Battersea. We went to that a lot. That was - I - was taken to see Faust and - several operas of that - type. And - comic operas they called them, musical comedies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Is that the same as music hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
No. No, that was the Grand at Clapham Junction. That was the - the music hall, that was variety with all these - old names that you might have come across Dan Leno and those people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go to music hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Mother took me. Yes. A woman called Gertie Getana, I saw her name not so long ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 They were the music hall stars?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go to any cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 There weren't any. No. The
re was a thing called the bioscope but I didn't go to it, but I did go to Kensington and - you sat in a coach - a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238 nd thought you were tearing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238  a - round, and seeing the scenery. I don't know what - what it was. Paid about four pence I think. That was before 
cinemas anyway. The first cinema I think I went to was when - a King died. Now when was that? Oh I can't remember when the cinema came, perhaps it was a bit earlier than I thought. Might have been. But of course we didn't go so much anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You went mainly to concerts and theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Mm. We used to have Sunday League Concerts. Now where were they? That was quite a good quality - concert at a - I don't know where it would be, or who the Sunday League were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Musical concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm. Singers and - orchestra and - musical instruments.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I wonder if that was anything to do with church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Don't think so, no. I think it would be somewhere - not the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238 Coliseum}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 , but - somewhere like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you belong to any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, I had about four}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 pence a week when I was ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What did you spend the money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I used to save it up to buy presents I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did anyone outside the home help your mother to look after her house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not when I was quite young, they did afterwards. We had a woman in to do a bit of cleaning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did she live in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No. Nobody lived in until mother was ill. We had a nurse then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 If your mother was ill or confined to bed for any reason, how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 She wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You said - did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, quite a number.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How much did they see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Quite a lot. I think that's who I played with you see, they were all cousins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not many, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were friends ever invited into the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not when I was a baby I don't think. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 But your relatives came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 They came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Frequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. They lived fairly near, within - quarter of an hour or - half an hour's walk some of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did neighbours ever come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time before 1918 did you think of so
me people belonging to one and some to another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well, yes, yes, there was the working classes, and there were the middle classes and the upper classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What sort of people would you say belonged to the working classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well the unformed staffs - for one. Labourers. Window cleaners.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And to the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What they - afterwards called the white collar - people. And professionals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were they called that then, white collar people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 By 1920 I suppose they were, I don't know about before that, it's a bit difficult to remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What about the other class, did you say the upper class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The upper classes, well they were the people in the expensive houses or - titled folk you know. Of course there weren't so many title
 folk in those days as there are now. They were a different class altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were the people just regarded in these three classes or w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 the classes divided up into different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you ever told to curtsey to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was there anyone you had to call sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well the - the - young boys would - automatically, but not the girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 In your area, around Battersea where you lived, do you know who were considered the most important people in the locality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I don't think there were many, there was John Burns the MP. He was a working class man you know, big Labourite. 
But - I can't think of anybody else actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Which class would you say you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well we were middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The shopkeepers, who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I suppose they came into the middle a bit, I'd - I didn't quite know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 The clergy and teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, well they'd be all middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
The middle. I think you'd call them middle class in those days. As they didn't earn much they couldn't afford a lot of money to spend and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What sort of people would you say went to the church and what sort went to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well there again - it was more - I think working classes that went to chapel. But - but probably not wholly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were there many Roman Catholics in your area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I didn't - I didn't know a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
In the are where you lived, did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living, or would you say there were different groups within the working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 class?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I should think they were all the same. More or less anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Yes, there were - there were rough labouring types. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Why were they rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - they lived in a - cheap fashion in a poor
 home, what's now more or less called a slum I should think there were some places in Battersea. And they - they didn't earn very much money, as I say, they were - very much labourers on the road and that sort. I suppose their upbringing made them rough.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I should think so, I don't - don't know of any reason why they wouldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh well, I think she thought herself above the working classes you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 That I don't know. Yes I think - Clapham - Common was a - a step up from Battersea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I used to meet some nice - people. But - I can't think of them at the moment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What did you think of him? How were police regarded in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh - ordinary I suppose, I didn't - I didn't think anything of him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you afraid of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know how he treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I didn't hear of - didn't hear that - he didn't treat them rightly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, the Battersea was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 They didn't have
 a lot of money but - there was no evidence of struggling I would say. See, money was so different, you can't - you couldn't imagine it. What it was like. Everybody was well dressed in my - circle. But you - you didn't have much money to spend. Things did
n't cost - and they lasted so well, they were - good material. Extraordinary now the - the stuff that's turned out. So that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So you mean that even if people didn't spend a lot of money on clothes what they had lasted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. They always used to sa
y I was well dressed. It didn't cost an awful lot and we weren't making, I mean nowadays - people make things, do you make things? No, but you know people who do, I mean, it doesn't cost a quarter of the price does it? Well we didn't do that. But of cours
e we didn't have so many clothes. Nothing like. Nothing like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 But you and your friends didn't make your clothes, you bought them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Ready made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes. Ready made. Yes, I suppose at - one time there were dressmakers. But - not so ma
ny. I expect I had something made but it - it wasn't usual anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of strongly was there any special way in which they showed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I never heard of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you given lessons by one of your parents?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What time in the morning did you have to go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Quarter to nine I - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm. Think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you come home for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh at the beginning I did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well was a - ordinary - you know, inexpensive school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mixed school for boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What did you think of school, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I can't remember. I just can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How many schools did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh not more than - two I shouldn't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you know what age you started your second school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. The usual age I expect. I - don't know what it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you remember anything outstanding about school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not a lot, no. I didn't dislike it I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What were the teachers like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Reasonably good. Liked - some I liked better than others. I was always good at reading.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did they emphasise certain things as important, like punctuality and tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I don't remember that, I suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What age did you leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Sixteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Can you - if any children did anything the teachers disapproved of what would happen to them in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Oh - they were - I suppose they were stood in a corner, it was never - happened to me, or you were sent to the - head of the firm. What happened then I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did all the other children come from similar sort of homes to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I think so. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would you have stayed on longer at school if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I learnt to - type, and write shorthand, and then I went to the Water Board. The first building was in - next door to the - Savoy}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4286619\charrsid5785238  H}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
otel in the Strand. And then after - a few months I was transferred to the - Southwark branch. And then the - head office was built a
t Roseberry Avenue next to the - theatre, and I stayed there. But during the war I went to a - a little place at Nerton, the Chairman said we must all get out from the head office because of bombing so we were spread about. But that didn't last long. We s
oon went back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So you were at the Water Board all your working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 All my life. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 When you started was it a Government concern?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, but similar. Similar, like Civil Service. We used to keep to the Civil Service - for salaries. Their level.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 I - wrote shorthand and did typing for a good many years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you secretary to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, they didn't have secretaries. We used to do all round the building. We'd be sent for and asked for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh it varied, I started with doing ten 'til five I think. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 At the age of sixteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Then when it - well I was older than that by the time - 'cos I went to - to learn shorthand typing first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 At a college or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
Yes, I went to - I went to an office, a typewriting bureau. I don't know whether there was a college at that time, but I learnt everything that you could ever learn in - typing and shorthand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How long did that take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well that was probably a - year or more I should think. Two years perhaps. I was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So you didn't start work 'til you were about eighteen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I - no, I was quite that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would you work on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Yes, we worked ten 'til
 one when I first went to Savoy Court. And then the hours changed and - I don't know what we made it, but this last war - we did - nine thirty 'til four. Because of the bombing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you enjoy this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm. Mm. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How did you get on with the boss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Pretty well. I was a good worker you see. Efficient. Good speller. Willing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So he must have enjoyed having you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 How many years were you in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Thirty-eight and a half. That staggers you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 And you were happy there all that time, you enjoyed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 After you started work, did you spend your leisure activities any differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well we had lots of thing
s up there. Because we had dances and whist drives and concerts and - all sorts of things you see. Football would give a dance and the rifle club would give a dance and the tennis club and the golf club. I went to the golf club supper. Organised by the Wa
ter Board, mm. But that was not when I first went. It would be a little bit later on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 So there was quite a lot of social life attached to your work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 A lot of social life, I used to go and - score for the cricket people sometimes when we had the inter-departmentals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you - so you met a lot of new people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 We had sport - annual sports every year, it was a big event.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you take part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not much, I - I - mostly I was on the committee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Were you very active in organizing social things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
I didn't - no, I - I didn't altogether organize - at one time I bought the prises with the secretary. And - saw to things a bit. You know, all sorts of - extraordinary how the things crop up but - I was always on the tennis club committee
 and - and the entertainments committee and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Is tennis your sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 It used to be, yes, I liked that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. Only that I always - voted, I never neglected to vote but I - I couldn't truthfully say I
 took an interest in it. I - it didn't seem to crop up like it does now. Things were rather different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 You couldn't vote for quite a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 No. No, I think I was twenty-one when I voted. I think I - think that was the age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Where did you get your political views from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Oh I only took them over from father. I didn't go anywhere to hear any other views.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you go out in the evening when you were working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well - well I didn't come home you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you bring any of your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Not a lot, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Well I can't ever remember that, but I think they were just disapproving if I was out late in the early days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 Did you have to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
I didn't - I - I was never told, I had a door key. I don't think they ever threatened. Of course my mother - got ill you know about - '37, '27 - 1922 I think she was in bed for fifteen years, it rather - quietened things at home, she had - what you now 
describe as a stroke and of course they hadn't got the - drugs and things so that - she never properly recovered. And - there was no National Health, it was a bit expensive. She was in a - nursing home I think for six months. And then she came home. And w
e
 had a trained indoor nurse for your years. We had a doctor every - week, unless something was - different, you know, and the we had him extra. Of course he charged seven and six a visit. And then I - I - I think it was after four years the nurse got marr
ied, but lived nearby so that she still came in.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6186984 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 But you managed to go on working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10616890 FJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10163806\charrsid5785238 
I - yes, two doctors said don't give up your job. But - it - I mean, we had no - entertainments at home much you see. No visitors much apart from the - few aunts came.
\par }}